#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:2 adfea8089e8b451fac3b8c0d9d963d5c
msgid "Poisson Equation"
msgstr "泊松方程"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:4 fab3558d19b14cea91e1348b3384d2e4
msgid ""
"Three scripts in ``examples/poisson/`` walk the Poisson problem through "
"TensorMesh's main features: a basic 2D solve, the same solver in 3D, and "
"h-adaptive refinement on an L-shaped domain whose re-entrant corner produces"
" a gradient singularity."
msgstr ""
"``examples/poisson/`` 中的三个脚本借助泊松问题展示了 TensorMesh "
"的主要特性：基础的二维求解、同一求解器的三维版本，以及在 L 形区域上的 h-自适应加密——该区域的凹角会产生梯度奇异性。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:9 6ca7af2b0cb54d2297d23f883099664b
msgid ""
"For batched right-hand sides over many source terms (the ML data- generation"
" pattern), see :doc:`dataset` — that script lives under "
"``examples/dataset/poisson/`` so all batched-RHS workflows sit in one place."
msgstr ""
"若需对众多源项进行批量右端项求解（即机器学习数据生成模式），请参见 :doc:`dataset`——该脚本位于 "
"``examples/dataset/poisson/`` 下，使所有批量右端项工作流集中于一处。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:14
#: dfb6c0a192ce496da2fc0ec66763b867
msgid "The strong form is:"
msgstr "强形式为："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:16
#: 7997110404e648b5a2fd2342447459e8
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"-\\Delta u = f \\quad \\text{in } \\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad u = 0 \\text{ on } \\partial\\Omega,"
msgstr ""
"-\\Delta u = f \\quad \\text{in } \\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad u = 0 \\text{ on } \\partial\\Omega,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:21
#: 2d01e03ee44c4393af55686cf6fd01dc
msgid "with corresponding weak form"
msgstr "对应的弱形式为"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:23
#: 77f894b887aa4910b8cdb6a10ae9516f
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\int_\\Omega \\nabla u \\cdot \\nabla v \\,\\mathrm{d}\\Omega\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"\\int_\\Omega f\\, v \\,\\mathrm{d}\\Omega\n"
"\\quad \\forall v \\in H^1_0(\\Omega)."
msgstr ""
"\\int_\\Omega \\nabla u \\cdot \\nabla v \\,\\mathrm{d}\\Omega\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"\\int_\\Omega f\\, v \\,\\mathrm{d}\\Omega\n"
"\\quad \\forall v \\in H^1_0(\\Omega)."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:30
#: 44a6fc8bf4fd458896e4cf7ae4bbe05d
msgid ""
"Every example below realizes this with "
":class:`~tensormesh.LaplaceElementAssembler` for the stiffness, a "
":class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler` for the load, and "
":class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` for the homogeneous Dirichlet BC. The ground-"
"truth source field comes from "
":class:`~tensormesh.dataset.PoissonMultiFrequency`, which generates a random"
" truncated Fourier series whose analytical solution is also available."
msgstr ""
"下面每个示例都用 :class:`~tensormesh.LaplaceElementAssembler` 实现刚度，用 "
":class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler` 实现载荷，用 :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` "
"处理齐次狄利克雷边界条件。真值源场来自 :class:`~tensormesh.dataset.PoissonMultiFrequency`\\ "
"，它生成一个随机截断的傅里叶级数，其解析解同样可用。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:40
#: 12f0e518ddda4c01bb9676c917d98169
msgid "Basic 2D Poisson — ``poisson.py``"
msgstr "基础二维泊松——``poisson.py``"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:42
#: d10d0a1f5fa5426c9b4b431a0bda2c47
msgid ""
"The shortest end-to-end driver in the repo. The full pipeline fits in 25 "
"lines:"
msgstr "仓库中最短的端到端驱动脚本。完整流程仅需 25 行："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:45
#: 43ed311655364bd1b0fdc722211b57fb
msgid "examples/poisson/poisson.py"
msgstr "examples/poisson/poisson.py"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:78
#: 37a9d74752584926ac327823140a6fe8
msgid "A few details worth pointing out:"
msgstr "有几处细节值得指出："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:80
#: d52c2c48d3504c3a97e314ceacc031b4
msgid ""
"``assembler(mesh.points)`` returns a "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` built from the gradient bilinear "
"form. Pure-Python weak form, no custom kernels."
msgstr ""
"``assembler(mesh.points)`` 返回一个由梯度双线性形式构建的 "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix`\\ 。纯 Python 弱形式，无需自定义核。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:83
#: 7b65af3b326b45a1974d578bf899fcc5
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"``FAssembler`` carries the source ``f`` through the integrand by name "
"(``point_data={\"f\": f}`` becomes the ``f`` kwarg in ``forward(v, f)``). "
"See :doc:`../user_guide/forms` for the full argument-dispatch contract."
msgstr ""
"``FAssembler`` 通过名称将源项 ``f`` 传入被积函数（\\ ``point_data={\"f\": f}`` 会成为 "
"``forward(v, f)`` 中的 ``f`` 关键字参数）。完整的参数分派约定参见 :doc:`../user_guide/forms`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:87
#: a7b9a76579d74a79bcce87ab4711740d
msgid ""
"The :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` shorthand ``K_, b_ = condenser(K, b)`` "
"applies the Dirichlet boundary mask and folds prescribed values into the "
"RHS. ``recover(...)`` glues the boundary values back on after the solve."
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` 的简写 ``K_, b_ = condenser(K, b)`` "
"会施加狄利克雷边界掩码，并将给定值并入右端项。\\ ``recover(...)`` 在求解后将边界值重新拼接回去。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:91
#: 505507f7d5ec4de0bb45f06a46d6b2e9
msgid ""
"``K_.solve(b_)`` is inherited from ``torch-sla``'s ``SparseTensor``; it "
"inspects the matrix and dispatches to the best available backend "
"automatically. Passing ``verbose=True`` prints that decision, e.g.:"
msgstr ""
"``K_.solve(b_)`` 继承自 ``torch-sla`` 的 ``SparseTensor``\\ "
"；它会检查矩阵并自动分派到可用的最佳后端。传入 ``verbose=True`` 会打印该决策，例如："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:100
#: 0b42be716f53448db0c239fe33053b80
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Here torch-sla detected a symmetric (but not SPD) system on CUDA and routed "
"it through cuDSS with an :math:`LDL^{T}` factorization. On CPU, or without "
"cuDSS installed, it falls back to a different backend; the ``backend=`` "
"field always tells you which one ran."
msgstr ""
"这里 torch-sla 在 CUDA 上检测到一个对称（但非对称正定 SPD）系统，并通过 cuDSS 以 :math:`LDL^{T}` "
"分解进行求解。在 CPU 上，或未安装 cuDSS 时，它会回退到其他后端；\\ ``backend=`` 字段总会告诉你实际运行的是哪个后端。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:105
#: f483b64a52244a94b86d23383c6d89a4
msgid "2D Poisson — source term, FEM solution, and analytical solution"
msgstr "二维泊松——源项、有限元解和解析解"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:109
#: da801c4d4fad4810b699b3c61a5f04ce
msgid ""
"Output of ``poisson.py``: source ``f`` (left), FEM solution ``u_fem`` "
"(middle), and analytical reference ``u_analytical`` (right) on the unit "
"square. The two solution panels are visually indistinguishable at this "
"resolution — exactly what you want from a converged mesh."
msgstr ""
"``poisson.py`` 的输出：单位正方形上的源项 ``f``\\ （左）、有限元解 ``u_fem``\\ （中）和解析参考解 "
"``u_analytical``\\ （右）。在该分辨率下，两幅解的图在视觉上无法区分——这正是收敛网格所应有的表现。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:117
#: 1e83b92840564268b5597517cbbd8d79
msgid "3D extension — ``poisson_3d.py``"
msgstr "三维扩展——``poisson_3d.py``"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:119
#: 107733c744934c309212df5b1e4e9ef7
msgid "Identical machinery, swapping in a tetrahedral cube:"
msgstr "机制完全相同，只是换用了四面体剖分的立方体："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:126
#: cc2b514de4ba4b828ba6cda5072e4563
msgid ""
"The same :class:`~tensormesh.LaplaceElementAssembler` works because "
"``∇u·∇v`` is dimension-generic — the integrand has no hard-coded spatial "
"dimension. The output is written as ``poisson_3d.vtu`` for opening in "
"ParaView; the script also produces a half-domain cutaway PNG for quick "
"inspection."
msgstr ""
"同一个 :class:`~tensormesh.LaplaceElementAssembler` 之所以适用，是因为 ``∇u·∇v`` "
"与维度无关——被积函数没有硬编码空间维度。输出写为 ``poisson_3d.vtu`` 以便在 ParaView 中打开；脚本还会生成一张半区域剖切的"
" PNG，供快速查看。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:132
#: 58193a7fac3447efa5be1f89ecc4521a
msgid "3D Poisson on the unit cube, half-domain cutaway"
msgstr "单位立方体上的三维泊松，半区域剖切图"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:137
#: 524b639adf3647789c4a54f2d97b0e15
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Output of ``poisson_3d.py``: half-domain cut at :math:`x=0.5` showing the "
"FEM solution on the unit cube. The reported mass-weighted relative "
":math:`L^2` error against the analytical Fourier solution is "
":math:`\\mathrm{rel\\_L2} = 1.059\\times10^{-2}` at ``chara_length=0.05``."
msgstr ""
"``poisson_3d.py`` 的输出：在 :math:`x=0.5` 处剖切的半区域，展示单位立方体上的有限元解。在 "
"``chara_length=0.05`` 下，相对于解析傅里叶解的质量加权相对 :math:`L^2` 误差为 "
":math:`\\mathrm{rel\\_L2} = 1.059\\times10^{-2}`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:145
#: 6beb7b9d7e5d4f77a5ca00c4de127dd4
msgid "h-adaptive refinement on the L-shape — ``poisson_h_adaptivity.py``"
msgstr "L 形区域上的 h-自适应加密——``poisson_h_adaptivity.py``"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:147
#: 05e7e23639c541a2b05158a51676e4f3
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"This is the one example on this page that goes well beyond the weak form. "
"The L-shaped domain has a re-entrant corner at :math:`(0.5, 0.5)`, where the"
" exact solution :math:`u = r^{2/3}\\sin(2\\theta/3)` has a gradient "
"singularity. Uniform h-refinement converges only at rate "
":math:`\\mathcal{O}(N^{-1/3})` because the global error is dominated by the "
"corner; an adaptive scheme that shrinks elements near the singularity "
"recovers the optimal :math:`\\mathcal{O}(N^{-1})` rate in 2D."
msgstr ""
"这是本页中唯一一个远超弱形式范畴的示例。L 形区域在 :math:`(0.5, 0.5)` 处有一个凹角，精确解 :math:`u = "
"r^{2/3}\\sin(2\\theta/3)` 在该处具有梯度奇异性。均匀 h-加密的收敛阶仅为 "
":math:`\\mathcal{O}(N^{-1/3})`\\ ，因为全局误差由该角点主导；而在奇异点附近缩小单元的自适应方案，可在二维中恢复最优的 "
":math:`\\mathcal{O}(N^{-1})` 收敛阶。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:157
#: 86e1e7ae425b45399b6a58bf6af06454
msgid ""
"The script implements the classical *solve → estimate → mark → remesh* loop:"
msgstr "该脚本实现了经典的 *求解 → 估计 → 标记 → 重剖分* 循环："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:160
#: 33ddc1a3de7e41d79c19bb15466bdb58
msgid "examples/poisson/poisson_h_adaptivity.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/poisson/poisson_h_adaptivity.py（核心）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:174
#: aa6f3542f47a4f079424763886eca7a7
msgid "Three pieces are worth a closer look:"
msgstr "有三处值得细看："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:176
#: c9f5c1f8e3bb41f3bef94cac811bdfe6
msgid ""
"**Non-homogeneous Dirichlet BC.** The exact solution is non-zero on the "
"boundary, so the script builds a :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` with "
"``dirichlet_value=g`` evaluated from the singular formula at every boundary "
"node. Static condensation folds the boundary values into the RHS; see "
":doc:`../user_guide/boundary_conditions`."
msgstr ""
"**非齐次狄利克雷边界条件。** 精确解在边界上非零，因此脚本构建了一个 :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser`\\ ，其 "
"``dirichlet_value=g`` 由奇异公式在每个边界节点上求值得到。静态凝聚将边界值并入右端项；参见 "
":doc:`../user_guide/boundary_conditions`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:183
#: 6d09e8957ff245a6891fa90415edcdf6
msgid ""
"**Mass-weighted error.** :class:`~tensormesh.MassElementAssembler` provides "
"the :math:`L^2` norm operator: ``e^T M e``. The relative error divides by "
":math:`\\sqrt{u_\\text{exact}^T M u_\\text{exact}}` for scale invariance."
msgstr ""
"**质量加权误差。** :class:`~tensormesh.MassElementAssembler` 提供 :math:`L^2` 范数算子：\\"
" ``e^T M e``\\ 。相对误差除以 :math:`\\sqrt{u_\\text{exact}^T M u_\\text{exact}}`\\"
" ，以获得尺度不变性。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:189
#: 3f9fc1abbcab4a1ca9d067f840f49881
msgid ""
"**Dörfler marking.** Mark every element whose error indicator exceeds "
":math:`\\theta\\, \\max(\\eta)` (default :math:`\\theta=0.5`) and halve its "
"size; coarsen the (almost-)error-free elements. The new size field is fed to"
" ``gmsh.model.mesh.setSizeCallback``, and the L-shape geometry is re-meshed "
"via OpenCASCADE booleans."
msgstr ""
"**Dörfler 标记。** 标记所有误差指示子超过 :math:`\\theta\\, \\max(\\eta)`\\ （默认 "
":math:`\\theta=0.5`\\ ）的单元并将其尺寸减半；对（几乎）无误差的单元则进行粗化。新的尺寸场被传入 "
"``gmsh.model.mesh.setSizeCallback``\\ ，并通过 OpenCASCADE 布尔运算对 L 形几何进行重剖分。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:195
#: 353f5253047e4c95b988364c54b6ebd3
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The output figure has three panels: convergence (adaptive vs uniform on a "
"log-log plot, with the :math:`\\mathcal{O}(N^{-1})` reference line), the "
"final adaptive mesh with elements clustered at the corner, and the FEM "
"solution itself."
msgstr ""
"输出图包含三幅子图：收敛性（双对数图上自适应与均匀加密的对比，并带有 :math:`\\mathcal{O}(N^{-1})` "
"参考线）、单元在角点处聚集的最终自适应网格，以及有限元解本身。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:202
#: d62427f964cf47c6ac8b6d29b961ef6d
msgid ""
"The remesh step calls into ``gmsh`` directly via the Python API and requires"
" ``gmsh >= 4.8`` for ``setSizeCallback``. Install with ``pip install gmsh``."
msgstr ""
"重剖分步骤通过 Python API 直接调用 ``gmsh``\\ ，并且 ``setSizeCallback`` 需要 ``gmsh >= "
"4.8``\\ 。请使用 ``pip install gmsh`` 安装。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:206
#: d2679d823ed049ec8f209b8359396638
msgid "L-shape adaptive vs uniform convergence, final mesh, FEM solution"
msgstr "L 形区域自适应与均匀收敛对比、最终网格、有限元解"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/poisson.rst:210
#: 9358a09f81f74b63a463c9dc8edb83ad
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Output of ``poisson_h_adaptivity.py``. Left: relative :math:`L^2` error vs "
"DOF count — the adaptive curve recovers the optimal "
":math:`\\mathcal{O}(N^{-1})` rate (dotted line) while uniform refinement "
"stalls at :math:`\\mathcal{O}(N^{-1/3})` thanks to the corner singularity. "
"Middle: the final adaptive mesh (757 DOFs) clusters elements at the re-"
"entrant corner. Right: the FEM solution itself."
msgstr ""
"``poisson_h_adaptivity.py`` 的输出。左：相对 :math:`L^2` 误差随自由度数的变化——自适应曲线恢复了最优的 "
":math:`\\mathcal{O}(N^{-1})` 收敛阶（点线），而均匀加密因角点奇异性停滞在 "
":math:`\\mathcal{O}(N^{-1/3})`\\ 。中：最终自适应网格（757 个自由度），单元在凹角处聚集。右：有限元解本身。"

